  "description": "\"smart\", \"focus\" → subliminal flash + ditzy distraction",
  "longDescription": "Catches \"smart\" words and fires opposing subliminals to nudge you back where you belong. Pairs a soft subliminal flash with a bimbo-coded avatar line. Two thematic jackpots — bubbles on 'study' and a mind-wipe on 'concentrate' — sit on long cooldowns so they stay special. Works hands-off; comments are better with AI on.",
